{"tid":1793522,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【唔可以慣！】 可唔可以針對性咁搞一場 \"反警暴、禁實彈\" 做主題既遊行/集會？","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T13:01:11.000Z","uid":20272,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9c3e82252766e24a1035fb9ea3c1d9ebc790da","tid":1793522,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">集思廣益</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日都多咗手足提到依個問題。<br />\n<br />\n搞依個遊行/集會目的如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 首要針對性令大眾唔好習慣依個現象。<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果現場又有Popo舉槍，就更令主題不辯自明。<br />\n<br />\n3. 五大訴求當然要搭單繼續講。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有其他提議請講，<br />\n總之要宣揚popo亂揸實彈槍依個問題！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1561c4da0827ab4a40665b6149928eea8383301e","tid":1793522,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85a3150a0f6345ae8315dd8ef18b58baa903edf","tid":1793522,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx